### Quartz Actuator Endpoints

# Get all Quartz jobs and triggers info
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/quartz
Accept: application/json

###

# Manually trigger a specific job (DEFAULT group, Qrtz_Job_Detail)
POST http://localhost:8080/actuator/quartz/jobs/DEFAULT/Qrtz_Job_Detail
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": "running"
}

### Dynamic Scheduling Endpoints

# 1. Schedule a new job named 'custom-job' to run every 5 seconds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/jobs/schedule?name=custom-job&intervalSeconds=5
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 2. Reschedule 'custom-job' to run every 2 seconds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/jobs/reschedule?name=custom-job&intervalSeconds=2
Content-Type: application/json

###

# 3. Schedule another job 'report-job' every 10 seconds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/jobs/schedule?name=report-job&intervalSeconds=10
Content-Type: application/json
